真源在本文；谁读谁写见 [23](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。** Host / 引擎只调 Port，**不**拼接下列路径。本机路径解释属 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":270,"content":"- Workspace 加载：`loadWorkspace` 经 ContentPort 装入 `scheduleCards`（本机 IO 扫 `characters/schedule-cards/*`）；**禁止**创建或 load `storis-packages/__schedule__/`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":324,"content":"4. 经 EngineLogPort 写 jsonl + 经 ProfilePort save Profile","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":334,"content":"注入：`createEngine({ freeCallPostPipeline })`。Story 卡仍走 Outcome → ExitSelector。存取注入见 [23 §5](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":457,"content":"**端口：** Host 经 `CreateEngineHostOptions.loreBootstrap` 注入 `LoreBootstrapPort`（Studio server 用环境变量装配 OpenAI 兼容 LLM；Key 仅 server）。成功写入 `source: \"llm\"`；无 port／无 Key／调用抛错 → `buildFallbackLore`（`source: \"fallback\"`）。单测用 mock port。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":478,"content":"| `data/logs/engine-YYYYMMDD.jsonl` | 事件 + error；**旁路**，不整份塞进 SaveGame；**持久化只经 EngineLogPort**（[23 §4.4](./23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":481,"content":"**WET 与 Profile：** 逻辑事件只走 ring + EngineLogPort→jsonl；**禁止**把整份 WET 写入薄 Profile／SaveGame。幂等权威在通话内 `CallSession.effectLedger`。Studio 受控追加仅 `wet.annotation`／`wet.compensation`（标注／补偿说明），**只追加不改写**既有行，禁止借追加篡改 effect 历史。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":14,"totalMatchedLines":14,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false,"headLimitApplied":30}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-0688a807-5a1d-4974-8d89-af86d8bd1a40-21\nfc_20d6f981-9dd4-9000-a586-373a75499517_7","startedAtMs":"1784786695205","completedAtMs":"1784786695358"},"model_call_id":"7e00fda9-003f-4713-bb4d-dd6638a4a66f-4-wodf","session_id":"ba9f1f4a-8af3-41d1-9254-1eee7937ded0","timestamp_ms":1784786695291}
